# iOS
ios/Pods/
**/Pods/
ios/build/
ios/*.xcworkspace
# Keep the xcworkspace if using expo prebuild with custom native code, but usually Pods are ignored. 
# However, standard practice often ignores the workspace content but keeps the file structure if distinct.
# For Expo managed workflow that is "prebuilt", we often ignore the whole ios/ and android/ folders.
# Since the user has ios, ios 2, ios 3, they likely have ejected or prebuilt.
# I will aggressively ignore Pods which is the source of the error.

